data.description: Beautiful turnkey home located close to the Pacific Crest Estates. This spacious 2,239 square foot home features 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths and a huge office, RV parking with 30 amp electrical service and dump station. Upon entering this stunning home, you’re greeted by an inviting front deck. Home features an open floor plan, large living room with cathedral ceilings, and a large fireplace with wood burning stove insert perfect for warming up a chilly Winter’s night. Home also features an updated kitchen with gorgeous granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas stove, double oven and large pantry. This country kitchen with a breakfast bar and dining area offers the warmth of the home.  Upstairs to the large master suite has a walk-in closet and plenty of windows for natural light. Bedrooms are large and office is even bigger. Office could be your den or fourth bedroom. Laundry room is conveniently located upstairs. Home features ceiling fans throughout, whole house fan and a large attic for storage. Solar panels are PAID in FULL and very efficient. Now outside to your private backyard with a sauna, covered deck and a concrete patio. Perfect for outside dining, entertaining and barbecuing. Backyard also features large shed and dog fenced area. Two car attached garage is great in the winter and so convenient.  This home has so many extras which makes it the perfect. Septic was replaced two years ago and home also offers a new water heater. Location is great for easy access to Hwy. 2 and Lone Pine Cyn.  Schedule your showing today
